GRWM to @toronto_fringe 2023!

I don't get to show my "normal" everyday looks but here it it! For those who don't me I'm actually an artsy kid yes those kids who went to those performing arts school lol.  So when i found out @toronto_fringe was hosting over 100 performances by different companies across Toronto I knew I had to attend! I attended 2 shows this week and it reminded me of how much I missed watching live plays and musicals. The festival is going on until July 16! So if you're in Toronto I highly recommend you attend a few shows! All info can be found at @toronto_fringe ! Support the arts !💜
